metadata.name: Mysterious World
metadata.description:
From birth, man is bound to the earth. But as soon as man sinks below the surface of the water, he is completely free

Freedom means to do what you enjoy, feel pleasure from.
These are the feelings you get, diving into the ocean, into the depths of an unknown and mysterious world.
In the realm of amazing and mysterious creatures.

Jellyfish is a symbol of tranquility and at the same time constant motion. It is elegance, harmony... It represents the concentration on your own self and the desire for peace of mind.

Pisces expresses the creative aspect of life, fertility and sexual
harmony
That's why they gently twirl around a woman's naked body .

The only copy
